  allNodes:
  - dialogueText: Greetings! Welcome the our hotel, what can I do for you?
    characterEmotion: 4
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389253
    - rid: 6774952781063389258
    - rid: 6774952781063389268
    - rid: 6774952781063389292
    isRootNode: 1
    editorPosition: {x: 276, y: 166}
    guid:
      Part1: 801923639
      Part2: 1285914272
      Part3: 169959312
      Part4: 2761389138
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: Thats odd... There's not much stuff to do around here
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389257
    - rid: 6774952781063389284
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1253, y: -408.24}
    guid:
      Part1: 2982223139
      Part2: 1084376014
      Part3: 4077460102
      Part4: 2544384999
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Fantastic! You can find your very own room number 2 upstairs,
      quite near our beautiful, temporarelly in reparations, sauna!

      Dinner
      will be served at 7pm'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389260
    - rid: 6774952781063389261
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1253, y: -51.23999}
    guid:
      Part1: 4028658863
      Part2: 1280522940
      Part3: 2166873217
      Part4: 985772993
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: "Oh, a few guests went in and decided to have too much fun! Ha-ha!
      \nDon't worry, they won't be invited again. We'll repair it as soon as we find
      the keys"
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389265
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2591, y: 152.76001}
    guid:
      Part1: 1012819177
      Part2: 1162638506
      Part3: 3147358645
      Part4: 705986296
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: I bet you'll be delighted. Our chef, Andrey, is such a fantastic
      cook, I just hope the pressure doesn't... agitate him...
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389264
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2591, y: -51.23999}
    guid:
      Part1: 3035836761
      Part2: 1265355892
      Part3: 2035803023
      Part4: 4244752949
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Oh you haven''t heard? We have some top tier guests this evening!

      Oleg,
      a politician in the midst of his campaign and Aleksei, a once quite popular
      artist'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389267
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 3681, y: -408.24}
    guid:
      Part1: 722697724
      Part2: 1280739601
      Part3: 1576957063
      Part4: 1757867502
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Right! He''s this pretty famous artist.

      Or at least he
      was...

      Now that I think of it I haven''t heard of any new paintings
      of his in a while.

      Maybe he got demotivated after that publication'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389286
    - rid: 6774952781063389287
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1179, y: 356.99997}
    guid:
      Part1: 2555944989
      Part2: 1144976354
      Part3: 2709672358
      Part4: 1246743225
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Well, yes! But as of late the hotel has been getting more guests
      than usual!

      And by "as of late" I do mean today...

      And by "usual"
      I do mean zero...'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses: []
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2260.996, y: -407.99994}
    guid:
      Part1: 3514762631
      Part2: 1103566297
      Part3: 3602503331
      Part4: 1515332628
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: Oh, I'd just hate to gossip!
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389288
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1962, y: 357}
    guid:
      Part1: 2145143534
      Part2: 1212596299
      Part3: 2942565505
      Part4: 1884612623
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Ok, fine I''ll tell you!

      Some reporter started spreading
      rumores about him being a sexual deviant! Gasp!

      And a homosexual one
      at that!'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389293
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2456, y: 357}
    guid:
      Part1: 3269285805
      Part2: 1082998990
      Part3: 3938144144
      Part4: 2440207961
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Not that I''ve heard, and you know how much I hate to gossip.

      Why''d
      you say so?'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389294
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2062, y: 567}
    guid:
      Part1: 1835650083
      Part2: 1116989002
      Part3: 330040960
      Part4: 909379228
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Oh let me guess, Oleg is jelous that Aleksei is getting the largest
      room, right?

      I knew it, I knew it, I knew it!

      I knew I had to
      find a way to make Aleksei liberate that room, there are hirearchies, you know?

      What
      will people say about my hotel if I can''t even give the best room to my most
      distinguished guest!'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389295
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2919, y: 567}
    guid:
      Part1: 1748450147
      Part2: 1172831568
      Part3: 623996333
      Part4: 1959634253
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Normally I would deny entry to such queer folk

      But, you
      have admit, the man is talented

      Oh how I dream of him making a painting
      with this hotel for all the world to see...'
    characterEmotion: 0
    characterReaction: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    isKey: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 6774952781063389296
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 3244, y: 357}
    guid:
      Part1: 3588371253
      Part2: 1297772373
      Part3: 2993961088
      Part4: 2788573545
